Posts.Content:
My wife had pain in her right breast and then we noticed that it was slightly enlarged. She went for a memmo and they told her that she has asymmetrical breast with slight dense or somethign to that effect - I wasn't there with her then. Now she is called back for an u/s. I am so nervous. enlarged breast with pain and feeling of fullness - Should we be worried about
 this? Please let me know if someone had similar symptoms.
Posts.Title: Asymmeteric breast - I am so nervous

Posts.Content: Thank you all for your responses. We went for another mammo and US. It turned out to be just dense tissue. All is fine. Thanks again you all.
